{
  "texts": [
    "Even during the interview, she maintains her systemic leader role by deciding that Gaby is too late, and, strikingly, I concur.",
    "Paula immediately turns to her phone to read Gaby's message aloud.",
    "At first sight, Paula appears to render Gaby's messages as they were written: she utters, \"Yeah, she is.",
    "I am in front 258 (.)",
    "I know it's late.\""
  ]
}